Hull Points: +22.5 → +54 (upgrades)
Acceleration: −0.3
Turn Acceleration: −0.75 deg/s²
Cost: 8,000
Durability: 6,000 / 6,000
Effect: Balanced composite hull module for Strike-class ships that increases both Armor Value and Hull Points, at the cost of reduced linear and turn acceleration. Good “all-rounder” survivability upgrade for fragile craft.
Upgrade Axis: Armor Value scales from +2.25 at L1 to +5.4 at L15; Hull Points scale from +22.5 at L1 to +54 at L15. Acceleration and turn-acceleration penalties remain fixed.

