Strike Damage Control (L1) – Active
Hullpoint Restore: +50 → +120 (upgrades)
Reload: 30 s
Power Cost: 50
Cost: 8,000
Durability: 6,000 / 6,000
Effect: Active hull repair system for Strike-class ships. On activation, instantly restores a chunk of Hull Points, consuming ship Power and triggering a 30-second cooldown. Best used reactively to survive burst damage or disengage.
Upgrade Axis: Hullpoint Restore scales from +50 at L1 up to +120 at L15. Reload time and Power Cost remain fixed at all levels.

Strike Engines

Engine Systems (Strike / Light Engine Slot, Passive)

Light Drive Overcharger (L1) – Passive
Boost Speed: +1.25 m/s → +3 m/s (upgrades)
Speed: +1.25 m/s → +3 m/s (upgrades)
Cost: 5,000
Durability: 6,000 / 6,000
Effect: Baseline Strike-class engine upgrade that provides flat bonuses to both cruise Speed and Boost Speed, improving general mobility without affecting acceleration or handling.
Upgrade Axis: Speed and Boost Speed scale from +1.25 m/s at L1 to +3 m/s at L15. No other stats change with level.

Light Turbo Boosters (L1) – Passive
Acceleration: +1 → +2.4 (upgrades)
Boost Speed: +2.5 m/s → +6 m/s (upgrades)
Cost: 5,000
Durability: 6,000 / 6,000
Effect: Strike-class engine module that enhances linear Acceleration and Boost Speed, improving sprint capability and responsiveness. Ideal for hit-and-run tactics and quick disengages.
Upgrade Axis: Acceleration scales from +1 to +2.4 at L15; Boost Speed scales from +2.5 m/s at L1 to +6 m/s at L15.

Light Gyro-Stabilization (L1) – Passive
Turn Speed: +2.5 deg/s → +6 deg/s (upgrades)
Turn Acceleration: +2.5 deg/s² → +6 deg/s² (upgrades)
Cost: 5,000
Durability: 6,000 / 6,000
Effect: Strike-class maneuvering module that increases Turn Speed and Turn Acceleration, making the ship more agile and responsive in tight dogfights. Does not affect linear speed.
Upgrade Axis: Both Turn Speed and Turn Acceleration scale from +2.5 at L1 to +6 at L15.

Light RCS Ducting (L1) – Passive
Avoidance: +15 → +36 (upgrades)
Cost: 5,000
Durability: 6,000 / 6,000
Effect: Strike-class RCS module that boosts Avoidance, making the ship harder to hit with cannon fire and other direct-fire weapons. No effect on speed or acceleration.
Upgrade Axis: Avoidance scales from +15 at L1 to +36 at L15.

T8 Drive Turbo Charger (L1) – Passive | Raven Mk VI-R Only
Speed: +3% → +7% (upgrades)
Boost Speed: +4% → +8% (upgrades)
Cost: 60,000
Durability: 6,000 / 6,000
Effect: Ship-specific engine upgrade for the Raven Mk VI-R Strike. Increases base Speed and Boost Speed by percentage, significantly improving flank and sprint performance without altering acceleration.
Availability: Usable only by the Raven Mk VI-R (Strike).
Upgrade Axis: Speed bonus scales from +3% to +7%; Boost Speed bonus scales from +4% to +8% by L15.

FoG Gyro-Stabilization System (L1) – Passive | Raven Mk VI-R Only
