Turn Acceleration: +10% → +16% (upgrades)
Cost: 50,000
Durability: 6,000 / 6,000
Effect: Advanced gyro system for the Raven Mk VI-R that increases Turn Speed and Turn Acceleration by percentage, delivering very sharp rotational control and tracking in dogfights.
Availability: Usable only by the Raven Mk VI-R (Strike).
Upgrade Axis: Turn Speed and Turn Acceleration scale from +10% at L1 to +16% at L15.

Translation RCS Thrusters (L1) – Passive | Raven Mk VI-R Only
