Availability: Usable only by the Raven Mk VI-R (Strike).
Upgrade Axis: Turn Speed scales from +10% to +20%; Strafe Speed scales from +15% to +24.5% by L15.

T15 Pulsed Plasma Thruster (L1) – Passive | Raven Mk VI-R Only
Boost Speed: +6% → +11% (upgrades)
Acceleration: +20% → +28% (upgrades)
Boost Cost: +25% (fixed)
Cost: 90,000
Durability: 6,000 / 6,000
Effect: High-end engine upgrade for the Raven Mk VI-R that substantially increases Acceleration and Boost Speed but raises Boost Cost, making sprinting more expensive in energy terms. Designed for pilots who value raw burst mobility over efficiency.
Availability: Usable only by the Raven Mk VI-R (Strike).
Upgrade Axis: Boost Speed scales from +6% to +11%; Acceleration scales from +20% to +28% by L15. Boost Cost penalty remains fixed at +25%.

Coupled RCS Ducting (L1) – Passive | Raven Mk VI-R Only
Avoidance: +4% → +9% (upgrades)
Boost Speed: −2.5% (fixed)
Cost: 62,000
Durability: 6,000 / 6,000
Effect: Defensive RCS upgrade for the Raven Mk VI-R that increases Avoidance at the expense of Boost Speed. Ideal for evasive, survivability-focused builds that prioritize not being hit over pure sprint performance.
Availability: Usable only by the Raven Mk VI-R (Strike).
Upgrade Axis: Avoidance scales from +4% at L1 to +9% at L15; Boost Speed penalty remains fixed at −2.5%.

FBS-12 Engine Overload System (L1) – Active | Rhino Only
Boost Speed: +16 m/s (fixed during effect)
Boost Acceleration: +3× (fixed during effect)
Boost Cost: +200% (fixed during effect)
Target: Self (Ignore)
Range: 0–0
Duration: 8 s → 16 s (upgrades)
Reload: 80 s
Power Cost: 60
Cost: 60,000
Durability: 6,000 / 6,000
Effect: Active overdrive system for the Rhino Strike that massively increases Boost Speed and Boost Acceleration for a short duration, at the cost of greatly increased Boost Cost and a long cooldown. Best used for emergency sprints, rapid repositioning, or high-risk attack runs.
Availability: Usable only by the Rhino (Strike).
Upgrade Axis: Duration scales from 8 seconds at L1 to 16 seconds at L15. Boost Speed, Boost Acceleration, Boost Cost, Reload, and Power Cost remain fixed.

Module Application Order (Strike Engines):

max_speed += sum(speed_bonus)
boost_speed += sum(boost_bonus)
lin_accel += sum(accel_bonus)
turn_rate += sum(turn_speed_bonus)
turn_accel += sum(turn_accel_bonus)
avoidance += sum(avoidance_bonus)

