Effect:
Escort-mounted strategic nuclear warhead designed to deliver catastrophic damage to Capital-class targets. Very high base damage and armor piercing, long effective range, and wide 180° launch arc. Constrained by slow reload and heavy power draw, making each shot a major commitment.

Upgrade Model:
Damage, maximum Range, and Reload time improve with level (shorter reload). Power Cost remains constant unless higher-level data show changes.

Implementation Notes:

Uses guided missile logic; warhead tracks like a slow but persistent torpedo (90 m/s, 30 deg/s turn).

Apply large explosion effects and potentially AOE vs nearby large ships, as desired for cinematic impact.

Intended primarily for use against Line/Capital ships; you can optionally give it reduced hit chance vs small targets.

Mark internally as “Nuclear”/“Strategic” to gate usage in missions and balance passes.

