Weapons (Medium / Heavy Hardpoints – Line Only)

MEC-L31(S) “Talon” — Heavy Cannon Battery (L1)

Damage: 35 – 70 (upgrades)
Armor Piercing: 35
Range: 0 – 1700 m
Optimal Range: 675 m (upgrades)
Accuracy: 125
Critical Offense: 100
Reload: 4 s
Power Cost: 25
Firing Arc: 180°
Cost: 20 000
Durability: 17 500 / 17 500

Effect:
General-purpose heavy cannon battery for Line-class ships.
Delivers substantial kinetic damage with long reach and a wide 180° firing arc.
High power draw and slow reload limit sustained fire; excels against armored or large targets at medium-long range.

Upgrade Model:
Increase Damage and Optimal Range per level. All other fields remain fixed unless higher-level data indicate otherwise.

Implementation Notes:

Uses standard ballistic hit, armor, and crit formulas.

Consumes full Power Cost instantly on fire; cannot re-queue until Reload completes.

Accuracy 125 is balanced for large targets (Line/Capital); less effective against Strike-class ships.

Apply standard range falloff using Optimal Range (peak DPS ≈ 675 m).

Restricted to Line-class hardpoints — enforce requirement in Store and Fitting UI.

